# Fixing Duplicate Logger Function Declarations

The error `Identifier 'initLogger' has already been declared` is occurring because the logging.js file contains two separate implementations of the same functions. Let's correct this by consolidating to a single implementation.

## Updates to c:\Dev\GitHub-Projects\onjs\public\js\utils\logging.js

This file needs to be updated to:
1. Remove duplicate function declarations
2. Keep the more advanced ClientLogger implementation
3. Maintain existing functionality

